== Ubuntu & Debian

sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev zlib1g-dev ruby1.8-dev build-essential ruby ruby1.8 rubygems
sudo gem install ruby-xml-smart (>= 0.2.1.1 needed)
sudo gem install rack mongrel mime-types
sudo gem install activesupport i18n

For websocket support /lib/ruby/server.rb includes a custom mongrel handler.

